metadata.name: Royal Bunny Sofia
metadata.description: Sofia is a bubbly bunny. Performing on stage is her dream because she loves to sing and dance. A confident and funny little princess. She is also a little bit clumsy.  She loves attention and is charming enough to get it.  Sofia loves to snack and nibble. Her tummy has to be full at all times or she will get grumpy. Her favourite snack is baby carrots.
